headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid ACN and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the last six months, Accenture’s shares have sunk to $320, producing a disappointing 9.3% loss while the S&P 500 was flat. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
